'''佛兰德海洋研究所'''（{{lang-nl|Vlaams Instituut voor de Zee}}，縮寫{{lang|nl|VLIZ}}；{{lang-en|Flanders Marine Institute}}）是位于[[比利时|比利时]]北部[[佛兰德|佛兰德]]的海洋科学研究中心<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.vliz.be/en/|title=Homepage|website=www.vliz.be|language=en|access-date=2018-05-30|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418173609/https://www.vliz.be/en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该研究所还代表弗拉芒政府支持和接待国际组织：[[政府间海洋学委员会|政府间海洋学委员会]]国际海洋学数据和信息交换项目办公室<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.iode.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=46&Itemid=84|title=International Oceanographic Data and Information Exchange (IODE) - International Oceanographic Data and Information Exchange (IODE)|last=Pissierssens|first=Peter|website=www.iode.org|access-date=2018-05-30|archive-date=2020-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200513044742/https://iode.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=46&Itemid=84|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=UNESCO/IOC Project Office for IODE|url=http://www.vliz.be/en/unescoioc-project-office-iode|accessdate=2021-01-24|work=www.vliz.be|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122085754/http://www.vliz.be/en/unescoioc-project-office-iode|dead-url=no}}</ref>，位于奥斯坦德的{{Link-en|欧洲海洋委员会秘书处|European Marine Board}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.marineboard.eu/|title=Homepage {{!}} European Marine Board|website=www.marineboard.eu|language=en|access-date=2018-05-30|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203192113/https://www.marineboard.eu/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和欧洲海洋观测和数据网络秘书处<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.emodnet.eu/|title=Central Portal|website=Central Portal|access-date=2018-05-30|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812071349/https://emodnet.eu/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及设在布鲁塞尔的健康和生产性海洋联合方案编制倡议秘书处<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.jpi-oceans.eu/|title=Home {{!}} JPI OCEANS|website=www.jpi-oceans.eu|language=en|access-date=2018-05-30|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417194241/https://www.jpi-oceans.eu/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

VLIZ还管理着一艘海洋研究船{{Link-en|研究船西蒙·斯蒂文|RV Simon Stevin}}号<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.vliz.be/en/rv-simon-stevin|title=RV Simon Stevin|website=www.vliz.be|language=en|access-date=2018-05-30|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412223305/http://www.vliz.be/en/rv-simon-stevin|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该研究所制定并主持了《[[世界海洋物种目录|世界海洋物种目录]]》<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.marinespecies.org/|title=WoRMS - World Register of Marine Species|website=www.marinespecies.org|language=en|access-date=2018-05-30|archive-date=2019-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190525041329/http://www.marinespecies.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和相关的分类分册，并主持了《[[海洋和非海洋属临时登记册|海洋和非海洋属临时登记册]]》<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.irmng.org/|title=Interim Register of Marine and Nonmarine Genera|website=www.irmng.org|language=en|access-date=2018-12-15|archive-date=2019-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190425171534/http://www.irmng.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[全球海平面观测系统|全球海平面观测系统]]的海平面监测设施。2011年11月，VLIZ被总部设在巴黎的[[国际科学理事会_(ICSU)|国际科学理事会 (ICSU)]]正式认定为世界数据中心<ref name=Marinespeciesorg>{{cite web |url=http://www.marinespecies.org/news.php?p=show&id=2860 |title=The Flanders Marine Institute (VLIZ), host institute of the WoRMS database, is now officially a World Data Centre. |date=2011-11-25 |accessdate=2012-03-23 |archive-date=2017-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171104101327/http://marinespecies.org/news.php?p=show&id=2860 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

